    "text_1": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>For two decades, J.Lindeberg and TRENDYGOLF have defined contemporary golf fashion, bringing performance-driven, stylish apparel to the fairways. Now, to celebrate this extraordinary partnership, the brands unveil the exclusive J.Lindeberg x TRENDYGOLF 20th Anniversary Capsule Collection. Featuring two limited-edition polo shirts in three striking colourways, dark green, deep blue, and beige, this collection reimagines classic J.Lindeberg styles with modern performance fabrics and bold, distinctive design elements. Available exclusively at TRENDYGOLF, this capsule is a testament to two brands that revolutionised how golf meets fashion.</p><h2></h2><h2><strong>A Partnership Rooted in Innovation</strong></h2><p>The story of TRENDYGOLF and J.Lindeberg is one of vision, persistence, and passion for redefining golf style. In 2004, two golf enthusiasts, Ian and Ben, were captivated by a fresh new look emerging on the PGA and European Tours. The stylish, athletic silhouettes worn by Swedish golfer Jesper Parnevik stood out against the traditional, conservative attire that dominated the sport. Upon discovering that the brand behind the revolution was J.Lindeberg, they faced an unexpected problem - finding a place to buy it. With limited availability and growing demand, Ian and Ben seized the opportunity to create TRENDYGOLF, an online destination dedicated to the most fashion-forward golf apparel.</p><p>From a niche online retailer to an internationally recognised institution, TRENDYGOLF has reshaped golf fashion by offering curated selections of premium, style-driven clothing. The company has become synonymous with bringing the latest golf styles to players seeking to elevate their game - both in performance and aesthetics.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
