    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "The Capsule Collection: A Tribute to 20 Years",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>To commemorate the shared journey, J.Lindeberg and TRENDYGOLF have developed a capsule collection that blends the past and present, featuring:</p><ul><li><strong>Modern Performance Fabrics:</strong> Each polo is crafted with J.Lindeberg's signature moisture-wicking, four-way stretch fabric, ensuring ultimate comfort and performance on the course.</li><li><strong>Refined Detailing:</strong> Clean lines, a sleek fit, and subtle design nuances reflect J.Lindeberg's Scandinavian heritage and commitment to high-end craftsmanship.</li><li><strong>Iconic Bridge Logo:</strong> A bold, oversized Bridge logo across the back of each polo pays homage to one of the brand's most recognisable design elements.</li><li><strong>Timeless Colour Palette:</strong> The dark green, deep blue, and beige hues reflect golf's rich traditions while maintaining a modern, versatile aesthetic.</li></ul><p><strong>Neil Lewty, Chief Creative Officer at J.Lindeberg, explains:</strong> <em>\"Looking back at the styles that defined J.Lindeberg's presence in golf, we wanted to create something that honours that legacy while staying true to our modern vision, blending timeless silhouettes with today's performance innovation.\"</em></p>"
          }
        }
      },
