          "settings": {
            "text": "A Milestone Marked on Tour",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>To mark the official launch of the capsule collection, J.Lindeberg ambassadors, including <strong>Matt Wallace, Camilo Villegas, and Niklas Norgaard</strong>, will showcase the limited-edition polos during the Valspar Championship from 17th-23rd March. Their presence on the course will further highlight the blend of heritage, innovation, and performance that defines the J.Lindeberg x TRENDYGOLF collaboration.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
