            "text": "<p>The J.Lindeberg x TRENDYGOLF 20th Anniversary Capsule launches exclusively at TRENDYGOLF on 20th March. With its perfect fusion of iconic design and modern performance, this collection is a celebration of two brands that have shaped the evolution of golf fashion over the past two decades.</p><p>For those who appreciate fashion-forward golf apparel, this is more than just a collection - it's a statement. A tribute to the last 20 years and a glimpse into the future of golf style. Don't miss your chance to own a piece of this exclusive collaboration.</p>"
